  "texts": [
    "Comparing text similarity across baselines and story periodUnder consideration of Eq. 12 and Eq.",
    "14, we assumed that story-supporting tweets can be only retrieved during the story period, while only irrelevant tweets can occur during baseline periods.",
    "We therefore expected lower text similarities for the baselines compared to the story period.",
    "We collected up to 10k tweets per baseline, depending upon how precise the respective query was for a given baseline.",
    "We used both linear mixed-effects modelling (LMEM) and receiver operating characteristic (ROC) analyses to quantify the differences in text similarity between baselines and story period.LMEM of mean text similarity across baselines and story period."
  ],
